86
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:39,440
the daily life of a real couple
after the announcement.

87
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,160
You two are also a popular couple.

88
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:41,840
Filming together

89
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:42,880
is an advantage for you too, right?

90
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:46,520
All departments, get ready.

91
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,720
Prepare to start filming.

92
