95
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,960
We'll see about that.

96
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:03,120
Bestie, I didn't think I'd see you here.

97
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,880
Yes, what a coincidence.

98
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:08,360
We happen to be on a date,
so we're leaving.

99
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,400
