106
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,560
- Yes.
- That's right.

107
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,160
We met because of this show.

108
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,440
Of course we should announce it
to everyone here.

109
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,480
We have two pairs of real couples.

110
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:37,200
