Why can't you get a single one?

113
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:07,720
This is my first time.

114
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:11,200
Lin Wan, I wanted to give you one

115
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:12,760
but Momo got these

116
