so I can't bear to.

117
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,160
I don't need it.

118
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,200
Stay focused.

119
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:19,960
You joined this show

120
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,120
to advertise for your hotel

121
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,400
while I'm here to make a name for myself.

122
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,560
We need to work together.

123
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:25,320
Would you believe me if I say
we only got 30 seconds' worth of footage

124
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:26,800
